Package: effect.size.wiz
Title: Customisable Effect Size Plots with Confidence Intervals for Scientific Presentations and Publications
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Fabian", family = "Schwendinger", email = "schwendinger.fabian@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person(given = "Eric", family = "Lichtenstein", email = "e.lichtenstein@unibas.ch", role = "aut")
    )
Description: This package provides functions to create customized effect size plots, visualizing confidence intervals with a speedometer-like design. It simplifies the interpretation of effect sizes in relation to their confidence intervals.
License: LGPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports: 
    ggplot2,
    viridisLite,
    grDevices
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Suggests: 
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
